    Interface and Description
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.ListenableScheduledFuture

  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.AbstractFutureCallbackFailureHandler
    Instead use a Consumer provided to ListenableFuture.failureCallback(java.util.function.Consumer)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.AbstractFutureCallbackResultHandler
    Instead use a Consumer provided to ListenableFuture.resultCallback(java.util.function.Consumer)
    org.threadly.concurrent.BlockingQueueConsumer
    See Poller.consumeQueue(java.util.Queue, java.util.function.Consumer) or BlockingQueueConsumer for replacement
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.FutureCallbackExceptionHandlerAdapter
    Instead provide the ExceptionHandler directly into ListenableFuture.failureCallback(java.util.function.Consumer)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.FutureCallbackFailureHandler
    Instead provide Consumer directly to ListenableFuture.failureCallback(java.util.function.Consumer)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.FutureCallbackResultHandler
    Instead provide Consumer directly to ListenableFuture.resultCallback(java.util.function.Consumer)
    org.threadly.concurrent.wrapper.PrioritySchedulerDefaultPriorityWrapper
    Moved to DefaultPriorityWrapper
    org.threadly.concurrent.RunnableChain
    Moved to RunnableChain
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.RunnableFutureCallbackAdapter
    To be removed without replacement, if you use this, open an issue on github
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.ScheduledFutureDelegate
    To be removed without public replacement, if used please open github issue
    org.threadly.concurrent.lock.StripedLock
    To be removed without replacement, if this is useful please file an issue on github
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.Watchdog
    Moved and renamed to ConstantTimeWatchdog
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.WatchdogCache
    Moved to MixedTimeWatchdog

  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.ListenableFuture.addCallback(FutureCallback<? super T>)
    Please use ListenableFuture.callback(FutureCallback)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.ListenableFuture.addCallback(FutureCallback<? super T>, Executor)
    Please use ListenableFuture.callback(FutureCallback, Executor)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.ListenableFuture.addCallback(FutureCallback<? super T>, Executor, ListenableFuture.ListenerOptimizationStrategy)
    Please use ListenableFuture.callback(FutureCallback, Executor, ListenerOptimizationStrategy)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.ListenableFuture.addListener(Runnable)
    Please use ListenableFuture.listener(Runnable)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.ListenableFuture.addListener(Runnable, Executor)
    Please use ListenableFuture.listener(Runnable, Executor)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.ListenableFuture.addListener(Runnable, Executor, ListenableFuture.ListenerOptimizationStrategy)
    Please use ListenableFuture.listener(Runnable, Executor, ListenerOptimizationStrategy)
    org.threadly.concurrent.CentralThreadlyPool.lowPriorityPool(boolean)
    use CentralThreadlyPool.lowPrioritySingleThreadPool() or CentralThreadlyPool.lowPriorityPool()
    org.threadly.concurrent.CentralThreadlyPool.lowPriorityPool(boolean, String)
    use CentralThreadlyPool.lowPrioritySingleThreadPool(String) or CentralThreadlyPool.lowPriorityPool(String)
    org.threadly.util.debug.ControlledThreadProfiler.removedProfiledThread(Thread)
    Please use ControlledThreadProfiler.removeProfiledThread(Thread)
    org.threadly.util.ExceptionUtils.runRunnable(Runnable)
    Please use SameThreadSubmitterExecutor.instance().execute(r) as an alternative
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.FutureUtils.scheduleWhileTaskResultNull(SubmitterScheduler, long, boolean, Callable<? extends T>)
    Please use FutureUtils.scheduleWhile(SubmitterScheduler, long, boolean, Callable, Predicate)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.FutureUtils.scheduleWhileTaskResultNull(SubmitterScheduler, long, boolean, Callable<? extends T>, long)
    Please use with a simple null checking Predicate FutureUtils.scheduleWhile(SubmitterScheduler, long, boolean, Callable, Predicate, long, boolean)
    org.threadly.concurrent.future.WatchdogCache.watch(ListenableFuture<?>, long)
    Please re-order arguments to use MixedTimeWatchdog.watch(long, ListenableFuture)
